This is the README file for Bundle::CPANPLUS::Dependencies.

Please refer to 'perldoc Bundle::CPANPLUS::Dependencies' after 
installation for details.

#####################################################################

* Description

Bundle::CPANPLUS::Dependencies

    Bundle to install all modules required & desired by CPANPLUS 
    
#####################################################################

* Installation

Bundle::CPANPLUS::Dependencies follows the standard perl module 
install process

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

The module uses no C or XS parts, so no c-compiler is required.

